*'''[[Luis' Van|1972 Ford Econoline]]''': In [[2015]], Luis got ownership of his family's van after his mother passed away and his father was deported out of the country. He then used it as his means of transportation and used it for heists with his friends [[Dave]], [[Kurt Goreshter]], and [[Scott Lang]]. He would often let them borrow his van. In [[2018]], he had the van rebranded as their company van.
