==Behind the Scenes==
*Due to the character's popularity, Luis was introduced into the mainstream Marvel Comics universe in the ''[[w:c:marvel:Astonishing Ant-Man Vol 1|Astonishing Ant-Man]]'' comic series.
*[[Michael Peña]] based his performance as Luis on his friend Pablo, who is a criminal.<ref>[https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DNbWln5vDZ0 Michael Peña Mimics His Criminal Friend Pablo for Ant-Man]</ref>
*[[Eric R Salas]], [[Tony Vella]] and [[Marlow Warrington-Mattei]] were stunt doubles for [[Michael Peña]] in the role of Luis.
*[[Moises Amaya]] was a stand-in for [[Michael Peña]] in the role of Luis.
*[[Joseph C. Nelson]] was a photo double for [[Michael Peña]] in the role of Luis.

